Question: The left and right image contains the same number of goat with at least one on the rocks.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/originals/cd/c1/37/cdc137a00b11aa0e6f38c5036edad343.jpg

Right image URL: https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ww_KeyWkbwM/UX0qED3YsGI/AAAAAAAAAsA/wQ3YcgR5vqM/s1600/400px-Capra_ibex.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many goats are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many goats are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there goats on the rocks?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there goats on the rocks?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
